---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import ascii from "../images/tacit-ascii.png";
---

<Layout title="Tacit Labs">
    <main
        class="p-gutter gap-gutter grid grid-cols-16 h-screen max-h-dvh relative overflow-hidden"
    >
        <div
            class="col-span-16 min-[700px]:col-span-8 min-[1695px]:col-span-7 flex flex-col grow justify-between mt-10"
        >
            <p
                class="font-mono font-light text-sm tracking-normal leading-normal"
            >
                Tacit enables frontier labs to develop LLM capabilities for the
                life sciences by collecting high quality data on how science is
                done.<br /><br />

                We imagine a future in which AI is a powerful tool for
                scientific discovery, capable of helping us reason through
                complex problems and driving optimal decision-making across
                discovery and development pipelines.<br /><br />

                Collaborating with biotechs and academic labs, we evaluate
                models on high-value, real-world tasks and works with frontier
                AI labs to systematically improve model performance on those
                tasks. Data collection will focus on outcome-verifiable,
                long-horizon planning and reasoning tasks to power the most
                critical functions in the life sciences.
            </p>
            <p
                class="font-mono font-light text-sm tracking-normal leading-normal"
            >
                Tacit is supported by <a
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alanagoyal/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Alana Goyal</a
                > at <a
                    href="https://basecase.vc/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Basecase</a
                >, <a
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/terrencerohan/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Terrence Rohan</a
                > at <a
                    href="https://otherwise.com/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Otherwise</a
                >, <a
                    href="https://soleio.cv/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Soleio</a
                >, <a
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/thomas-wolf-a056857/"
                    class="underline">Thomas Wolf</a
                > (<a
                    href="https://huggingface.co/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Hugging Face</a
                >), <a
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jonathan-frankle/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Jonathan Frankle</a
                > (<a
                    href="https://www.databricks.com/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">MosaicML</a
                >), <a
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/matthew-leavitt/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Matthew Leavitt</a
                > (<a
                    href="https://www.datology.ai/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Datology</a
                >), <a
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/danshipper/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="underline">Dan Shipper</a
                > (<a href="https://every.to/" target="_blank" class="underline"
                    >Every</a
                >), and others.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 translate-x-[20%] translate-y-[20%] opacity-30 -z-10 pointer-events-none"
        >
            <img
                src={ascii.src}
                alt="Tacit Labs ASCII"
                class="h-[clamp(32rem,50vw+30vh,96rem)] w-auto max-w-none"
            />
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
